	"system": {
		"description": {
			"value": "<p><em>Sorcerers with the draconic origin are almost always descended from dragons. Since dragons can change shape and take mortal form, it's not unheard of for mortal bloodlines to have a draconic ancestor. In some, the power of the draconic bloodline manifests as powerful magical abilities that only grow with use.</em></p><p><em>In the world of Elkan, being part of a draconic Bloodline means you cannot be part of another, and you will forever have impulses to act similarly to the personalities of your Bloodlines. While you can control these impulses, it is a lifelong struggle. For more information, see the description of any dragonborn ancestry, such as @UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-ancestries.Item.CgP9p46fONndLjgp]{black dragonborn}.</em></p><table><caption><p>The Draconic</p></caption><thead><tr><th scope=\"col\"><p>Level</p></th><th scope=\"col\"><p>Features</p></th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><p>1</p></td><td><p>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.2JklRbZrpjBkItBR]{Draconic Toughness}</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>3</p></td><td><p>Breath Weapon</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>6</p></td><td><p>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.87UBpH3dq0GLt31o]{Frightful Gaze}</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>10</p></td><td><p>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.mWzkmsjC9Vq9nLHD]{Blindsight}</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>14</p></td><td><p>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.sJitRqcpmEgWIFtE]{&amp;reference[dragon] Wings}</p></td></tr></tbody></table><table><caption><p>Expanded Spell List</p></caption><thead><tr><th scope=\"col\"><p>Sorcerer Level</p></th><th scope=\"col\"><p>Extra Spells</p></th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><p>1</p></td><td><p><em>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.xwb82OAnypYUZ5BO]{Command}</em></p></td></tr><tr><td><p>3</p></td><td><p><em>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.qiiRiG2gsOxO89Jm]{&amp;reference[dragon]'s Breath}</em></p></td></tr><tr><td><p>5</p></td><td><p><em>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.GBsOYscOZmOZy0Ff]{Fear}</em></p></td></tr><tr><td><p>7</p></td><td><p><em>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.IXTamgZ9OiDPEu0v]{Fire Shield}</em></p></td></tr><tr><td><p>9</p></td><td><p><em>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.JMvciQxc508dJ3t8]{Dominate}</em></p></td></tr></tbody></table>",
			"chat": ""
		},
